This document provides an overview of the various documents and links that are part of this project's general information. All of this content is automatically generated by Maven on behalf of the project.

Overview

Document Description
About Gapa is a command line application that connects to a websocket server. The server sends messages to gapa. The messages contain data about HTTP communication between nodes. The data may be filtered and is converted into a sequence diagram in PlantUml format.
